擇數種格率拍攝，並進一步提供更多手動調整選項，包含觸控自動對焦、白平衡調整等，加上Sony獨特的智慧風聲過濾技術，提供用戶更完整、專業的影像創作空間。<br />\n<br />\n006: 6.5 吋 21:9 CinemaWide 4K HDR OLED螢幕搭配導演模式Creator mode（powered by CineAlta），呈現前所未見的精準色彩<br />\n<br />\n007: 與 Sony Pictures Entertainment 合作精心調校的Dolby Atmos 杜比全景聲音效，於觀看影音時創造絕佳的立體環繞音效體驗。透過與Sony Music Entertainment 合作，調校出音樂人期望的理想高音質，搭配立體聲喇叭，加入最新 360 Reality Audio實境音效，DSEE Ultimate 數位音質還原技術，帶來逼近真實、媲美原音重現的聆賞體驗。<br />\n<br />\n008： 21:9寬螢幕手遊體驗有PlayStation 4 的 DUALSHOCK 4 遊戲手把，讓行動遊玩體驗更歡樂，「遊戲增強器」新增全新功能，支援Competition Set專注模式，提供遊戲應用程式置頂設定，創造極致手遊體驗。<br />\n<br />\n009：新世代5G高速傳輸結合高通Snapdragon 865 處理器，搭載大容量4000mAh電池及無線充電功能，創造最佳速率和效能，帶來前所未見的遊戲、攝影、多工處理、高速連線等優異表現。<br />\n<br />\n010:搭載極其先進嘅3.5mm插口"},{"pid":"ff1cf4743892087be0b79785d839ee739c292203","tid":1945559,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b482fee7887f18b143cd4da6dc2852f3f8aaca5d","tid":1945559,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/45444665_1182510341913450_208886971391541248_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Kqj_6Movpn8AX8i06ZE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=de8d6425820cdfa63387b673bef0b03c&amp;oe=5EA52FFE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F45444665_1182510341913450_208886971391541248_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DKqj_6Movpn8AX8i06ZE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Dde8d6425820cdfa63387b673bef0b03c%26oe%3D5EA52FFE&h=7f37fc94&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"高清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea34be2d7f0cc8dc6234b89ced12209303c98ffb","tid":1945559,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b482fee7887f18b143cd4da6dc2852f3f8aaca5d","tid":1945559,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https:/